title: End Game
description: When the worst-case scenario becomes reality, all the Lucky Charms in the world can’t solve our problems. Just when Luke started to open up, he closes himself off again.When we first met, he assured me he was no Prince Charming. I’m starting to believe him.And then tragedy strikes.This can go one of two ways. Either he’ll lean on me the way a husband should lean on a wife, or he’ll push me away. But I’ve got a little secret of my own, and I have no idea what it means for our end game.  END GAME is the final book in the VEGAS ACES series. This series must be read in order. author: Lisa Suzanne
